            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-1690285288416-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-1690285288416-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-copy-1690285288416-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>hake fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper and add them to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray with the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong>, then put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1690285295375-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1690285295375-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1690285295375-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1690285295375-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-1690285295375-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and roughly chop the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley </strong>and <strong>basil </strong>roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Slice the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>in half and cut 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> wedges and set them aside for serving</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1690285301945-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1690285301945-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1690285301945-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1690285301945-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1690285301945-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>parsley </strong>and <strong>basil</strong> to a <strong>pestle & mortar</strong> and grind to a coarse paste</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese </strong>directly into the mortar and continue to grind together to make a paste</p><p>Drizzle over enough<strong> olive oil</strong> to loosen the mix, then add a squeeze of<strong> lemon juice </strong>and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>pesto</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't have a pestle & mortar? Pulse in a food processor instead!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1690285307186-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
