        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>hake fillets</strong> over the<strong> lemon mash</strong> with the<strong> cherry tomatoes </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle a little <strong>pesto</strong> over the fish and serve the rest to the side</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
